---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';
import MarkdownContent from '../../../components/MarkdownContent.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Regional Equipment 2026 - East Malaysia',
  slug: 'regional-equipment-2026-east-malaysia',
  excerpt: 'Regional equipment financing 2026. East Malaysia Sabah, Sarawak equipment loans.',
  date: '2026-01-06',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 3,
  category: 'Equipment Financing',
  image: '/images/blog/regional-east-malaysia.jpg'
};

const keywords = ["machinery-financing","east-malaysia","regional"],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];

const markdownContent = `
# Regional Equipment 2026 - East Malaysia

Regional equipment financing for East Malaysia (Sabah, Sarawak) in 2026.

## East Malaysia Equipment Needs

**Regional Markets:**
- KK, Kuching, Miri, Bintulu
- Resource industries
- Infrastructure development
- **Equipment demand growing**

## 2026 East Malaysia Financing

**Regional Considerations:**
- Delivery time: 5-7 days
- Installation support
- Service network
- **Local dealer partnerships**

## East Malaysia Interest Rates

| Location | Rate | Notes |
|----------|------|-------|
| **Sabah** | 5.0-5.5% | KK, Sandakan, Tawau |
| **Sarawak** | 5.0-5.5% | Kuching, Miri, Bintulu |

## Get East Malaysia Equipment

Sabah or Sarawak business? Apply for regional equipment financing.

